Such part or parts of the area herein declared open for disposition, which are being used or earmarked for public or quasi-public purposes shall be excluded from such disposition. Except in favor of the Government or any of its branches or agencies, all lands disposed of under this proclamation shall not be subject to alienation and encumbrance for a period of ten (10) years from the issuance of title, in case of sale, or execution of contract, in case of lease, nor shall they become liable to the satisfaction of any debt contracted prior to the expiration of the said period; but the improvements on the land may be mortgaged to qualified persons, associations, partnerships or corporations.

An Inter-Agency Committee, composed of representatives of the Department of Environment and Natural Resources (DENR) as Chair, Housing and Urban Development Coordinating Council (HUDCC), Department of Transportation and Communication, Presidential Commission on the Urban Poor, City Government of Davao and concerned non-government or people’s organizations is hereby created to immediately implement this proclamation.

IN WITNESS THEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 23 rd day of September, in the year of Our Lord, two thousand and two.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

